courses.entryRequirements: A completed undergraduate degree (or equivalent) + meet English language requirements. English (typical course requirement): IELTS 6.5 overall with Writing 6.0 (atau TOEFL iBT ~81 with corresponding sub-scores). Indonesia (SMA): calon Indonesia harus memenuhi persyaratan nilai SMA (rata-rata pada 6 mata pelajaran kelas 12) dan persyaratan bahasa Inggris; jika belum memenuhi syarat akademik, pathway diterima melalui Foundation providers yang diakui (mis. Trinity College Foundation Studies).
courses.fees: See course fees page on study.unimelb.edu.au (current international tuition shown on course fees page)

courses.entryRequirements: Recent secondary education (VCE/IB/A-levels) or recognised equivalent. Entry is selection-rank (ATAR) based for domestic; international applicants (Indonesia – SMA) must meet required Year 12 averages (rata-rata nilai 6 mata pelajaran kelas 12) and English language requirements; prerequisites may apply for some streams. Jika belum memenuhi syarat SMA, pathway yang diterima termasuk program Foundation yang diakui (mis. Trinity College Foundation Studies).
courses.fees: See course fees page on study.unimelb.edu.au for current indicative international tuition.

courses.entryRequirements: Course is primarily domestic (lihat ketersediaan); untuk detail entry dan apakah tersedia untuk internasional, periksa halaman kursus. Trinity College Foundation Studies) dapat menjadi opsi untuk masuk ke program sarjana terkait.
courses.fees: See course page for fees and international availability.
